reviewText:
This review is very difficult due to prejudiced reviews all over the world. Before any conclusions, keep those words in mind.

In this game...

1. You can perform Head Shot and Hat Shot in one game; they are all HS, anyways...
2. You'll hear Rambo original movie theme every 30 seconds throughout gameplay;
3. Rambo looks like a Fallout 3 bubblehead;
4. All enemies are  Josh Brolin  [www.imdb.com] clones, wearing Elizabethan collar as hats;

This game...
5. Would be a great game in 1992;
6. Would have come with a Menacer or Super Scope 6 or Zillion in a box, along with the game;
7. IS NOT FPS... it is on rails shooter that is VERY different and is described in game info on store;
8-10... When I finish the game I'll think about it :D... maybe

For now, I'm having fun with the game but it is far from a diamond in the rough"... In general

♥♥♥♥↗ YOU↓

